00:05:35.140 --> 00:05:52.213
categories of biomolecules.
We have, first of all, proteins.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:49.830
Carbohydrates,

00:05:49.830 --> 00:05:55.490
nucleic acids and lipids.
And, in the three lectures that we

