so you cannot use it now.

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:54.400
And, when both enantiomers are
present, this is called racemic.

00:19:54.400 --> 00:20:12.200
And this is very important, as I
said it is a matter of life and

00:19:40.800 --> 00:19:47.200
death, in pharmaceuticals.
I will tell you one example.

